name: Michele Sturt
seeking: Seeks JV partners who serve the diabetes and chronic illness community — particularly those who can refer individuals frustrated with conventional disease management and looking for a lifestyle-based coaching alternative. Would benefit from partnerships with diabetes educators, endocrinologists, integrative health practitioners, or patient advocacy groups willing to recommend wellness-focused coaching support. Co-marketing with chronic illness influencers or functional medicine platforms would help reach individuals actively seeking a holistic approach to diabetes management.
who_you_serve: Individuals with diabetes seeking holistic wellness coaching, disease management support, and lifestyle transformation.
what_you_do: Coaches individuals managing diabetes through lifestyle and wellness strategies.
offering: Delivers professional services and strategic solutions through mydiabeteasecoach.
business_focus: Coaches individuals managing diabetes through lifestyle and wellness strategies.
